                                                   2nd spot up for grabs
            A STAFF REPORTER                      
	Calcutta: Its the battle for the No.2 spot in the LG ICC Test Championship table as South Africa take on India in a three-Test series starting Wednesday. If South Africa win the series 1-0 or 2-1, they would displace India from second place. A drawn series of any kind (0-0 or 1-1) or an Indian win would ensure the second spot for hosts, according to an ICC release.         
